quran[25]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,43,"Indhahoodu hoos u rogan yihiin, dulli baa dabooli; waxaana loogu yeedhi jirey inay sujuudaan iyagoo fayow(mase yeelin)."
  68,44,"Isu kaana daa Aniga iyo kuwa beeniya warkan (Qur’aanka); waxaan ka qaban si heerar ah meel aysan ka fileyn."
  68,45,"Waan u seeto dheereyn, hubaal, tabteydu waa mid sugan oo adag."
  69,40,"Kani waa hadal (Ilaahay) uu keenay Rasuul sharaf leh (Nabi Muxammad s.c.w.)"
  69,41,"Ma aha hadal gabyaa, yaraa intaad rumeysaan."
  69,42,"ama hadal curraafle, yaraa intaad waantowdaan."
  70,34,"Ee ah kuwa xafida oo dhowra salaaddooda,"
  70,35,"Kuwaasi waxay geli Beeraha Jannada iyagoo sharfan."
  70,36,"Muxuuse arrinkoodu yahay kuwaa Xaqa diida waa iyaga u soo degdega hareerahaada’e."
  72,28,"Si uu u muujiiyo inay run ahaan gaarsiiyeen Farriimihii Rabbigood, (Allena) wuu koobay waxa agtooda ah, wayna u tira kooban yihiin wax walba."
  74,19,"Nacaladi ha ku dhacdee! Siduu wax u qorsheeyey."
  74,20,"Misna, nacladi ha ku dhacdee, siduu wax u qorsheeyey."
  74,21,"Kaddib wuu eegay;"
  75,16,"Ha ku dhaqaajin (Nabiyow) carrabkaaga (markuu Waxyigu soo degayo) inaad ku degdegto (Qur’aanka akhrintiisa)."
  75,17,"Waa xil Annaga na (saaran) inaan ku kulminno (laabtaada, ku xifdisiinno) oo kuu (sahalno) akhrintiisa (iyo fahankiisa)."
  75,18,"Ee markaan akhrinno (Jabriil kuu akhriyo) u raarici (maqalka) akhriskiisa."
  76,10,"Waxaan ka cabsan Rabbigayo (Allaah) Maalin (wajigu) doorsoomi, murugo badan."
  76,11,"Sidaa awgeed Alle wuxuu ka samata bixin sharka Maalinkaas, oo siin nuur iyo farxad."
  76,12,"Oo ku abaal marin sabarkooda dartiis Janno iyo xariir."
  77,7,"Ee waxa (dadow) la idiinku yabooho ( Qiyaamada) waa Xaq dhacaya."
  77,8,"Marka xiddiguhu beelaan nuurkooda;"
  77,9,"Oo samadu dildillaacdo,"
  78,4,"Mayee, way ogaan doonaan (waxa ku dhaca beenintooda Xaqa darteed)."
  78,5,"Misna, mayee way ogaan doonaan (waxa ku dhaca)."
  78,6,"Miyaanaan ka yeelin dhulka gogol?"